fig3A <- ggplotify::grid2grob(plot(clade_forest))

figure3 <- plot_grid(fig3A,fig3B,fig3C,labels = "AUTO",nrow=3,label_size = 18,rel_heights = c(1,1,1),label_x = 0,align = "hv",axis='l')
